reviews.text:
Just really surprised to make our revisiting after 5 or 6 years!👏 
Love the Smoked Salmon Salad and the Creamy Risotto. I really get used to visiting the extremely good stores in the alleys and the lanes. 
The strange scenario in Hong Kong is that the good shops are really sparse in the downtown area. So just go ahead and make your very first visit to the hidden gems herein.🥰
Great value of money and super friendly staff
While this Italian restaurant is not easily accessible, food quality is good and also affordable. I recommend pizza and pasta.
Food quite alright, service good too...
Food is quite good. Service is all right. The night we went there were a lot of take away orders and the kitchen didn't seem to be able to cope so the wait for the food was extra long.

reviews.text:
Just really surprised to make our revisiting after 5 or 6 years!👏 
Love the Smoked Salmon Salad and the Creamy Risotto. I really get used to visiting the extremely good stores in the alleys and the lanes. 
The strange scenario in Hong Kong is that the good shops are really sparse in the downtown area. So just go ahead and make your very first visit to the hidden gems herein.🥰
商場地方大，商店購物品牌撰擇多，不愁吃喝玩樂，而且隣近零碳天地添，很適合一家大細玩一整天；唯交通比較不便，但不失為一處的地方。
服務員有禮貌， 食物也不錯， 再來都有水準
食物質素不俗，地方面積比較細
肉類質素不俗，沙律新鮮份量足。客人多的時候，食物質素會下降
